{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "78c60392",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "（あぁ……ダメ、またムラムラしてきてる……オナニーしたばかりなのに……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ccbb7188",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あの日、クンニされて以降、{G_PlayerName}のことが気になって仕方がない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.0",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86349587",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あの甘美な光景を思い出してしまうだけで欲情してしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.2",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "86349587",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "自分を慰める日々が続く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6a9e9658",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "でもどれだけオナニーをしても満足するのはその直後だけ……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "12952e66",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すぐにまたムラムラしてしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.2",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "12952e66",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして今も股間をくちゅくちゅと弄ってしまっている。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.0",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9ba6e3f9",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "（廊下であんなことされたのに……誰かに見られたかもしれないのに、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.2",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9ba6e3f9",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "それなのに彼のことが……こんなに誰かを想ってしまうなんて初めて……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.0",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3968f270",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "（わたし、強引に求められるのが好きだったの……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.2",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3968f270",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "だからこんなに心奪われて……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5abc93d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}に強引に求められているいやらしい自分の姿を妄想し、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.2",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5abc93d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "全身が熱くなり、そして子宮が甘く疼く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c81d7206",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何度も何度も唇を奪い、そして乱暴に胸を揉む彼の荒々しい姿を想像する。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.2",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c81d7206",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それだけで愛液が洪水のように膣穴から溢れ、息が荒くなってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fba0b4bf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして彼は発情しきったわたしをさらに求める──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e5317aff",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "あぁぁ……！♥　ダメ、こんなところでぇ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.2",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e5317aff",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "誰か来てしまう……見られてしまう……♥　うう……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.0",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1edf897f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こんなにおまんこぐちょぐちょにして何言ってんだ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.2",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1edf897f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "チンポ突っ込んでほしいんだろ？　おまんこ掻き回してほしいんだろ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "12d655e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "中出しされて絶頂したいんだろ？　孕ませられたいんだろ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "76c125e2",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "そ、そんなこと……望んでなんてぇ……あひぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6d170fff",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}の限界まで勃起した逞しい肉棒がお尻の間に挟まり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.2",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6d170fff",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その熱さに腰が大きく跳ね上がる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.0",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "58446497",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼はわたしをさらに発情させるように、お尻で肉棒を扱き、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.2",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "58446497",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒を求めるあそこがさらに愛液溢れ、床に大きな水たまりを作る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fd4c4343",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "くくく……相変わらず良い声で鳴く女だ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.2",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fd4c4343",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ほらほら、もっと鳴け、ほかのメスに聞こえるくらい喘げっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.0",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7241a03f",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "だ、めぇ……あんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.2",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7241a03f",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "あの子達にに聞かれてしまう、キミとセックスする関係だってバレてしまう……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b981d62a",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "わたしは……あの子達の先生なのに……あひぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.0",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bc08b466",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "はははっ、お前のようなメス豚が先生なんてあいつらが可哀想だなっ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.2",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bc08b466",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "どうせならつまんない授業なんてやめてセックスを教えたらどうだ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "26878a64",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんなら俺が先生やってもいいぞ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.2",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "26878a64",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "子作りの授業をしてやる。あいつらの前でお前を犯してやるぞ？　くくくくっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "82a68184",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼は容赦なく耳元でわたしを罵る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.0",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "961cf08e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな{G_PlayerName}の言葉にわたしはさらに高ぶり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.2",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "961cf08e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "言葉だけで絶頂しそうになるくらい感じてしまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7c266961",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "くく、そろそろオマンコも限界のようだな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.2",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7c266961",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ほら、これ欲しいんだろ？　欲しいって言えよっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.0",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6a2a5f12",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "ひいいっ！♥　ああ、おちんちん……うあ、あああーっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "81c1cb47",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ナノ、お前は俺の女だ、俺だけのメス奴隷だ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.2",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "81c1cb47",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お前はもう俺だけのことを考えろ、俺だけのことを想って四六時中発情してろっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.0",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21036491",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "はうううっ！♥　んんぅぅっ！♥　ああぁぁ～～っ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bc4b1954",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼はまるで物でも扱うように、男根を容赦なく膣の中に押し込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.0",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ae35974e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "くくくっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.2",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ae35974e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんの抵抗もなくチンポ受け入れて……やはり犯して欲しかったんだなっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.0",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fbf6330",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "ち、違う……犯してほしい、なんて、思ってないぃ……あうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "78c89cef",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ウソをつくなクソビッチ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.2",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "78c89cef",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こんなのオマンコぐちゅぐちゅにしやがって。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.4",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "78c89cef",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "まったくお前のオマンコはたまらねーなっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f79a587c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼はわたしのお尻を叩くように腰を打ち付け、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.2",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f79a587c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぢゅぶりといやらしい音と、肌のぶつかり合う音が部屋中に響く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b56f00c3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "荒々しい逞しい腰の動きに、膣奥の疼きが強くなる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a1f4f99",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そしてわたしの胸も高鳴ってしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.2",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a1f4f99",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼を求めるように腰を押し付けてしまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.0",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f7c8d57a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "良い悲鳴だっ！　よほどほかの女に聞かれたいらしいな？なら望み通りにしてやるっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.2",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f7c8d57a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "おらっ！　鳴け鳴けっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2c68120",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "んひぃぃぃっ！♥　ダメぇっ！♥　あ、ぁぁっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.0",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87b4234d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼の男根のカリが膣壁を容赦なく擦り上げ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.2",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "87b4234d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "亀頭の先端が子宮を押しつぶす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "adf35093",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "甘く強烈な快感の連続に、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "adf35093",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頭の芯まで蕩けるような気持ち良さに襲われる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.0",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "42164bb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思考は{G_PlayerName}に襲われることだけを望んでしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.2",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "42164bb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "表向きは彼を拒否しても、内心では彼に媚びを売る様に求めてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eaa63d0f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "くくっ！　オマンコ震えてきたな。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.2",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "eaa63d0f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そろそろ一発目の精液くれてやるか……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4d03c5a7",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "ああ、中はダメ……！♥　赤ちゃんデキちゃう！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.2",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4d03c5a7",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
      "ja": "今日はダメな日なの……！♥　それだけは許してぇぇっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cdb44671",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ははははっ！　それは良いことを聞かせてもらったぜ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.2",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cdb44671",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ならしっかり子宮に注ぎ込んでやらないと、なっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7e3e8cb1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼は乱暴にわたしの身体を引っ張り、さらに肉棒を膣の奥へ押し込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "156.0",
      "line_index": 156,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2ea95ad9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "抵抗する意思をまったく示さない子宮口は、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "156.2",
      "line_index": 156,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2ea95ad9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "彼の大きな男根を咥えこむように吸い付く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.0",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f053feff",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "くははっ！　ダメダメ言ってるクセにオマンコは正直だなっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.2",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f053feff",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "しっかり孕ませてやる……責任なんてとらねーからなっ！　ナノせんせ～！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.0",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6bb5d17a",
      "speaker": "ナノ",
